<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span><span class="c4">[اليَرْبُوعُ]</span>: معروف،<span class="c5"> والجمع:</span> يرابيع.<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
